5 A BILL
6 TO BE ENTITLED
7 AN ACT
8
9 Relating to the National Guard; to amend Sections
10 31-10-2, 31-10-3, and 31-10-4, Code of Alabama 1975; to
11 authorize tuition assistance for workforce development
12 programs through the National Guard Educational Assistance
13 Program; to authorize assistance payments through the program
14 earlier in the academic term; to authorize the State Military
15 Department and Alabama Commission on Higher Education to
16 jointly administer the program; and to repeal Section
17 31-10-4.1, Code of Alabama 1975, relating to qualifications
18 for the National Guard Educational Assistance Program.
19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
